<br>
I mean wtf ?? One, you're stupid for trying to charm something you knew you couldn't yesterday.  Two snare the damn rats and run your ass to zone. OR snare the rats, run to camp, root 2 away, let one come to camp and I'll kill it.  Keep the other 2 rooted and I'll get them once I've recovered.  <br>
<br>
I mean is it just me or should this be common frickin sense ????<br>
<br>
Issue #7  I could be totally off here on this one, and if I am I apologize, but for the life of me I had no frickin idea what this druid was talking about... Can't get in group in POD so decide to start soloing.  Notice big spiders open, so start looking for a 60+ druid to duo them with.  Send tell to druid LFG.<br>
